AÇIKLAMA
|--> Konfigürasyonlarda kullanılan (DHCP ve SLAAC witch DHCP yöntemlerinde) DHCP sunucusunu da L3 switchler üzerinde konfigüre ettim. DHCP istemcileri öncelikle ip bilgilerini nasıl alacağını routera soruyorlar. Nasıl alacaklarını öğrendikten sonra DHCP üzerinden alacağı bilgiler varsa (bizim labaratuvarımız için) tekrar routera gelerek ip bilgilerini talep ediyor. Kafa karışıklığı yaratmayacağını umuyorum.


DHCPv6 Server Konfigürasyonu
**********************************************************
CE6800-1
----------------------------------------------
system-view
sysname CE6800-1
commit

dhcpv6 enable
dhcpv6 duid llt

dhcpv6 pool Pool1
address prefix 2001:ABCD:FFFF:CCCC::/64    
excluded-address 2001:ABCD:FFFF:CCCC::1 to 2001:ABCD:FFFF:CCCC::50
dns-server 2001:FBFB:FBFB:FBFB::10
quit

int ge 1/0/1
undo portswitch
ipv6 enable
undo sh
ipv6 address 2001:ABCD:FFFF:CCCC::1/64
dhcpv6 server Pool1
quit

commit








DHCPv6 Only SLAAC Konfigürasyonu
**********************************************************
CE6800-1
----------------------------------------------
system-view
sysname CE6800-1
commit

dhcpv6 enable
dhcpv6 duid llt

int ge 1/0/1
undo portswitch
ipv6 enable
undo sh
ipv6 address 2001:ABCD:FFFF:CCCC::1/64
ipv6 nd ra halt disable
quit

commit






DHCPv6 SLAAC with DHCP Konfigürasyonu
**********************************************************
CE6800-1
----------------------------------------------
system-view
sysname CE6800-1
commit

dhcpv6 enable
dhcpv6 duid llt

dhcpv6 pool Pool1
dns-server 2001:FBFB:FBFB:FBFB::10
quit

int ge 1/0/1
undo portswitch
ipv6 enable
undo sh
ipv6 address 2001:ABCD:FFFF:CCCC::1/64
ipv6 nd ra halt disable
ipv6 nd autoconfig other-flag

dhcpv6 server Pool1
quit

commit







DHCPv6 DHCP Konfigürasyonu
**********************************************************
CE6800-1
----------------------------------------------
system-view
sysname CE6800-1
commit

dhcpv6 enable
dhcpv6 duid llt

dhcpv6 pool Pool1
address prefix 2001:ABCD:FFFF:CCCC::/64    
excluded-address 2001:ABCD:FFFF:CCCC::1 to 2001:ABCD:FFFF:CCCC::50
dns-server 2001:FBFB:FBFB:FBFB::10
quit

int ge 1/0/1
undo portswitch
ipv6 enable
undo sh
ipv6 address 2001:ABCD:FFFF:CCCC::1/64
ipv6 nd autoconfig managed-address-flag

dhcpv6 server Pool1
quit

commit














DHCPv6 Relay Agent Konfigürasyonu
**********************************************************
CE6800-1
----------------------------------------------
system-view
sysname CE6800-1
commit

dhcpv6 enable
dhcpv6 duid llt

dhcpv6 pool Pool1
address prefix 2001:ABCD:FFFF:CCCC::1/64
excluded-address 2001:ABCD:FFFF:CCCC::1 to 2001:ABCD:FFFF:CCCC::50
dns-server 2001:FBFB:FBFB:FBFB::10
quit

int ge 1/0/0
undo portswitch
ipv6 enable
undo sh
ipv6 address 2001:ACAC:ACAC:ACAC::100/64
ipv6 nd autoconfig managed-address-flag
dhcpv6 server Pool1
quit

commit



CE6800-2
----------------------------------------------
system-view
sysname CE6800-2
commit

dhcpv6 enable
dhcpv6 duid llt

int ge 1/0/0
undo portswitch
ipv6 enable
undo sh
ipv6 address 2001:ACAC:ACAC:ACAC::1/64
quit

int ge 1/0/1
undo portswitch
ipv6 enable
undo sh
ipv6 address 2001:ABCD:FFFF:CCCC::1/64
ipv6 nd autoconfig managed-address-flag
dhcpv6 relay destination 2001:ACAC:ACAC:ACAC::100
quit

commit



